  "markup": "\u003Cp class=\u0022p1\u0022\u003EWant to know how Super Pulsed Laser can treat conditions from head to toe? This is the must-see webinar! We cover difficult conditions including carpal tunnel, frozen shoulder, back pain, plantar faciitis and much more.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg height=\u0022505\u0022 alt=\u0022April 2013 LTU Webinar\u0022 width=\u0022590\u0022 src=\u0022~/media/950ABD9A5537411381C437947967C4F2.ashx\u0022 /\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
